"title": "2428: gospel, descriptions of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2428: gospel, descriptions of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The beauty, authority and importance of the gospel can be seen from the way it is described in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>In the Gospels</h2>\n<h3>As good and joyful news</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14\">MRK 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:10-Luke2:11\">LUK 2:10–2:11</a></p>\n<h3>As being of heavenly origin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:16-John17:18\">JHN 17:16–17:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28\">JHN 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49-John12:50\">JHN 12:49–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10\">JHN 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:24\">JHN 14:24</a></p>\n<h3>As words of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:63\">JHN 6:63</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:11-John3:15\">JHN 3:11–3:15</a></p>\n<h3>As being complete and gloriously rich</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:25-Col1:27\">COL 1:25–1:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:12-Rom10:13\">ROM 10:12–10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8\">EPH 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>In the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7-Isa52:10\">ISA 52:7–52:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9\">ISA 40:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:27\">ISA 41:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:15\">NAM 1:15</a></p>\n<h2>In the NT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:11\">1TI 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16-Rom1:17\">ROM 1:16–1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:15\">ROM 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:6\">REV 14:6</a></p>",
